sequenceDiagram
    actor Operator
    participant Feed as AthenaFetcher
    participant Sent as AthenaSentiment
    participant Eng as AthenaEngineer
    participant Fusion as SignalFusion
    participant MTF as MTFGate
    participant Risk as AthenaRisk
    participant Router as AthenaRouter
    participant Writer as StatsWriter
    participant UI as Streamlit Dashboard

    Feed->>Eng: batch {ohlcv, orderbook}
    Sent->>Eng: sentiment snapshot
    Eng->>Fusion: engineered features
    Fusion->>MTF: AthenaSignal(direction, confidence)
    MTF-->>Fusion: allow/block + reason

    alt Blocked by MTF
        MTF->>Writer: mtf_blocks++, last_mtf_reason
        Writer->>UI: refresh live_stats.json
    else Passed MTF
        Fusion->>Risk: risk.check(signal)
        alt Blocked by risk or size
            Risk->>Writer: risk_blocks++, size_blocks++, reason
            Writer->>UI: runtime diagnostics update
        else Approved and opened
            Risk->>Router: size + SL/TP plan
            Router-->>Risk: order/trade result
            Risk->>Writer: pnl, balance, orders_opened
            Writer->>UI: telemetry + trade history
        end
    end

    Operator-->>UI: presets / overrides
    UI-->>Fusion: weights
    UI-->>MTF: filter toggle
    UI-->>Risk: min_confidence
